00:17:01 --> 00:17:04
and civil society and governments tomorrow.

166
00:17:04 --> 00:17:11
Africa’s progress will depend on development
that truly lifts countries from poverty to

167
00:17:11 --> 00:17:22
prosperity -- because people everywhere deserve
the dignity of a life free from want. A child

168
00:17:22 --> 00:17:26
born in Africa today is just as equal and
just as worthy as a child born in Asia or

169
00:17:26 --> 00:17:32
Europe or America. At the recent development
conference here in Addis, African leadership

170
00:17:32 --> 00:17:38
