187
00:19:03 --> 00:19:09
for hydropower, you can turn this climate
threat into an economic opportunity. And I

188
00:19:09 --> 00:19:14
urge Africa to join us in rejecting old divides
between North and South so we can forge a

189
00:19:14 --> 00:19:19
strong global climate agreement this year
in Paris. Because sparing some of the world’s

190
00:19:19 --> 00:19:25
poorest people from rising seas, more intense
