204
00:20:51 --> 00:20:58
but also freedom of speech and the press,
freedom of assembly. These rights are universal.

205
00:20:58 --> 00:21:07
They’re written into African constitutions.
(Applause.) The African Charter on Human and

206
00:21:07 --> 00:21:12
Peoples Rights declares that “every individual
